}
```

and `Z3_mk_const()` doing almost exactly what I'm doing here except also calling the function `save_ast_trail()` which I cannot seem to access from the new API.

I would appreciate any assistance you can provide with respect to how to generate fresh theory variables / constants from inside my theory plugin.

